sequenceDiagram

    participant U as User
    participant M as MAUI App
    participant A as ASP.NET API
    participant R as RAG Service
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant L as LLM Service
    participant G as Gemma 4

    U->>M: Ask financial question

    M->>A: Chat request

    A->>R: Query

    R->>P: Vector search (pgvector)
    P-->>R: Relevant notes/context

    R->>P: Fetch transactions

    P-->>R: Structured financial data

    R->>L: Prompt + Context

    L->>G: Generate response

    G-->>L: Answer

    L-->>R: Response

    R-->>A: Final answer

    A-->>M: Chat response

    M-->>U: Display answer